es were so outrageous they could not possibly be worn on the street.</p><p>In 2007 Ulvaeus was wrongly accused of failing to pay 85m kronor (£7.9m) in Swedish taxes between 1999 and 2005, and went on to successfully appeal against the decision.</p><p>\"I am of course very happy that I have been informed in writing that I have always done the right thing concerning my taxes,\" he said after the court victory.</p>","headline":"Abba admit outrageous outfits were worn to avoid tax","trailText":"New book reveals band's style was influenced by Swedish laws that allowed cost of outfits to be deducted against tax","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/3mnpd","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/2/16/1392577441790/Abba-006.jpg","wordcount":"216","liveBloggingNow":"false"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/feb/16/abba-outfits-tax-deduction-bjorn-ulvaeus","apiUrl":"http://internal.content.guardianapis.com/music/2014/feb/16/abba-outfits-tax-deduction-bjorn-ulvaeus","tags":[{"id":"music/abba","webTitle":"Abba","type":"keyword","sectionId":"music","sectionName":"Music","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/music/abba","apiUrl":"http://internal.content.guardianapis.com/music/abba","references":[]},{"id":"fashion/fashion","webTitle":"Fashion","type":"keyword","sectionId":"fashion","sectionName":"Fashion","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/fashion/fashion","apiUrl":"http://internal.content.guardianapis.com/fashion/fashion","references":[]},{"id":"music/music","webTitle":"Music","type":"keyword","sectionId":"music","sectionName":"Music","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/music/music","apiUrl":"http://internal.content.guardianapis.com/music/music","references":[]},{"id":"world/sweden","webTitle":"Sweden","type":"keyword","sectionId":"world","sectionName":"World news","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/world/sweden","apiUrl":"http://internal.content.guardianapis.com/world/sweden","references":[]},{"id":"lifeandstyle/lifeandstyle","webTitl